cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with the problem of estimating the orientations of nodes in a pose graph, which is a common problem in robotics and computer vision. Therefore, cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also presents an algorithm that computes a set of estimates with probabilistic guarantees, which suggests that it may belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with optimization problems, which suggests that it may also belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
